DESCRIPTION:The Moore Theatre is located in downtown Seattle at 1932 2nd Av
	e\, Seattle\, WA 98101. There is an overall 9 ticket limit per patron. Pat
	rons exceeding the ticket limit will have their orders canceled at the ven
	ue's discretion. Mobile barcodes delayed until 4 days prior to event. Venu
	e reserves the right to change delivery methods. All sales are final. No r
